<script>
$(document).ready(function() {
    class_names = ["rapid_gtm_class", "octavia_gtm_class", "yeti_gtm_class", "superb_gtm_class", "stock_gtm_class"];
    for (var i = 0; i <= 4; i++) {
        $li = $(".bmmMenuMain.noindex li:nth-child("+(i+1)+")");
        $li.addClass(class_names[i]);
    }
});
</script>

<script>
$(function(){
$('.bmsMenu a').click(function(){
  var href = $(this).attr('href');
  if(href.indexOf('.pdf') > 0) {
    ga('send', 'event', 'PDFDOWNLOAD', 'DOWNLOAD', href);
    console.log('Tracking event', 'PDF download', href);
  }
})
});
</script>
